Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:30.03,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:37.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:44.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:51.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:01:00.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.24,0:01:05.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.57,0:01:10.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.53,0:01:16.38,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:22.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号告别后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 娜蒂亚与大王 搭乘飞机来到岛屿上空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却突然遭到不名人士攻击 而迫降于森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们在那里认识了 住在岛上的小女孩 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉的双亲 已遭神秘组织杀害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝三人组 也被那个组织抓了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们虽然也遭到攻击 但总算是逃了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隔天早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强与娜蒂亚 将玛莉双亲的死讯告诉了她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但玛莉却不懂那所代表的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:04.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个人也下定决心 要保护这名小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:09.78,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#06 孤岛要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉的家旁边 有一间很大的教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是在这一带吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每个星期天我都会跟爸爸妈妈 一起去祈祷喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 玛莉真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:02:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,教堂的位置大致吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人型战车在拉着车？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是车子在操纵人型战车吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小孩们尚未出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女孩子要留活口 知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回去你的岗位\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小孩们？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是在找我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女孩子要留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,指的应该是娜蒂亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来是港口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,北方在上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那条就是玛莉说的路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,港口？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 有很多船停靠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我知道喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从教堂旁边的路直直走 就能看到很多船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸常带我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,戒备还真森严
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本溜不进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好惊人的货物量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且这里的电量也好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴黎也没亮成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是从哪里输送来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝着山里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那座山里会有什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不晓得吗？ 妈妈都会亲我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好睡吧 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈都是说『晚安 玛莉』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗…对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚安 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论村里还是港口 全都是那群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还是向人求助…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们上哪找人帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们全都是杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该还有没被他们发现 躲了起来的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们就跟那些人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你告诉我那些人在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛 就会胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你要我怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你应该要想个更…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们是在夫妻吵架吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 对不起 不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧的 你别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 靠我们两个 根本逃不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加上还有个玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对不能让玛莉遇上危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:08:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,基地的中心应该就在 岛屿中央的露天矿坑里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了晚上我会再去查探情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以跑出去 会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好美的花园
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以 强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,潜入对方基地太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想被抓住的人 应该都被关在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听我说 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们对这座岛的认识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只有问玛莉而画出来的 这张地图而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须潜入基地 取得更多情报才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经想好潜进去 也不会被发现的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不去冒这个险 是无法离开这座岛屿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黄色的 白色的 红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很漂亮吧 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要为牧克做一条 天堂最美的项圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我帮你摘吧 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:29.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是现在去了 大家都会被抓住的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:10:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们正在等 看有没有人会去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好奸诈的一群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来没有其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 全员准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定会去救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看到烟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密基地应该就在那下头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉与大王就在那里是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要把他们救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.29,0:11:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是利用以前的坑道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好亮的灯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么时候发明的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我跟鹦鹉螺号借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这条输电线路 应该会通到他们的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,据玛莉所说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里有间大发电厂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那这里头有许多电啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个带有相当强大的电压
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,随便乱碰会被烧成焦炭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是出口吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于到他们的大本营了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们都是岛上的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是湖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个就是秘密基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,八成是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个就是火力发电厂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好多烟囱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正中央的塔会是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来又不像天线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闪闪发着光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是座玻璃塔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么用途呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一头的那个是城堡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.21,0:13:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这地方还真惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,密密麻麻都是管子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么的工厂呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你什么都不晓得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得再到下面去调查才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是输送带
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是要输送什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干不下去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来她在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 那边的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.22,0:13:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在做什么 还不快点干活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别在那边唠唠叨叨的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己过来挖如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然逼我这种 娇弱的少女做苦工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身为男人你知不知羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这混帐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不费吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们还挺行的嘛 让我刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都快进入 20世纪的科学时代了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种苦工实在跟不上潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这东西先借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们就快点开溜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然你们那么讨厌工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就带你们去个好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是要邀请我们参加晚餐会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以 会场就在地下监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮你们举办 不吃不喝的盛大派对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是淑女耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能对我客气点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢蛋 给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 这条输送带停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别让它停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要从这种地方下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走在上头会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们要沿着这些管子 到城堡去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样会弄得浑身都是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法啊 又不是来野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也对 这是为了玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停…停下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛死我了 怎么突然就动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那只海中怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.90,0:16:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那果然是潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是它将我爸爸的船…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有人走出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地位似乎很高
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恭候您的大驾 石像鬼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经掌握人质 很快就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无论使出怎样的手段都无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,组织规模似乎相当庞大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰？ 会是什么意思呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是熔矿炉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜…娜蒂亚 下面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快逃到下面去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,掉下去会粉身碎骨的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抓住我 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人造山铜调整得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比预定迟了0.01%
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但还是来得及在实验前完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好热喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,忍耐点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一到外头马上会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但万一要是掉下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们会连渣都不剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别这样吓我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好热喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们是将石英熔化 做成玻璃砖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是要做什么用呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就只会想那些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相当现代化的自动工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头没半个工人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却有看守的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夜里看守的人应该会少一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时再…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时再躲到那边的输送带下面 慢慢前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,按照以上所言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,此人造山铜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乃集合我们目前所有科学力量 所得到的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就理论上而言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它应该能展现 如同预料之中的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光有理论只是纸上谈兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必须实际用得上才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得 这还是第一次这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前并未出现类似情况
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快去调查
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许是在对什么东西产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚的『蔚蓝之水』？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那边 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点 往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 光芒消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了 在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再不停下来就要开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧 只是擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道你们在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.42,0:22:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们已经被团团包围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,高举双手乖乖出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像可以通到其它地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出去之后 你就拿着这个逃到那个洞里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只数到五
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.62,0:22:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由我出去 你就趁机…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.66,0:22:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些家伙要抓的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.46,0:22:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:22:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我一定会回来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,三
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,四
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢着 别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那名女孩 要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快追 别让她逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,往那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别让她跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.02,0:23:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.12,0:23:54.68,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.76,0:24:02.92,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:07.90,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.97,0:24:12.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.37,0:24:21.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.25,0:24:31.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.39,0:24:40.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.17,0:24:44.40,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.47,0:24:49.07,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.14,0:24:58.25,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.96,0:25:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 我一点都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.67,0:25:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.27,0:25:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…强一定会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.07,0:25:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.38,0:25:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,石像鬼为什么会称呼我为公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.85,0:25:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.05,0:25:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『巴别塔』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.62,0:25:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
